  "body": "An absolute killer feature for `hardhat` would be a similar thing like `jest --coverage` : \r\n\r\n`npx hardhat test --coverage` \r\n\r\nI am aware of `hardhat-toolbox` and `npx hardhat coverage`. \r\n\r\nHowever, unlike the `solidity-coverage` plugin this should support generating coverage reports for contracts that use `delegatecalls` to run their implementation's code (e.g. Upgradeably Proxy contracts or Diamonds). \r\n\r\nSo essentially I am asking you to modify `solidity-coverage` to add support for delegatecall coverage too :) ",
